snippet.title: WILL HOGE: "Even If It Breaks Your Heart"  +  12.13.2012
snippet.description:
Will Hoge performing his 2013 Grammy-nominated song, "Even If It Breaks Your Heart" at The Down Home in Johnson City, TN on 12/13/2012, the final stop of his "Let Me Be Lonely Tour." You may recognize the song as being the Eli Young Band's #1 hit from 2012.

Dear YouTube: All rights to Will Hoge. I have known Will for almost 15 years, and was sitting directly in front of him when I recorded this video (which I claim no rights to). Will knows I recorded this video. He encouraged posting video to YouTube throughout his set. He has always been a proponent of his fans sharing his music. So please, leave this video alone.
